<P><H1 align=center>DC210 – NEW PROPERTY ADDRESS</H1>
<P></P>
<P>Collects address details of the new property to be mortgaged.</P>
<P><H3>Post code: </H3>Input the new postcode and click on 
<STRONG>P.A.F Search </STRONG>button. The system will check through it’s post 
code directory and list all the properties registered under that post code. 
Select the property required and click on select, this will populate the address 
in the relevant address fields. Click on the <STRONG>Clear </STRONG>button to 
delete all address fields.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Arrangements for access: </H3>Select the appropriate 
persons with whom access to the property has been arranged (for the purposes of 
the mortgage valuation visit) from the drop down list.
<P></P>
<P>If the Vendor is selected, click on the <STRONG>Vendors 
details </STRONG>          button, and input 
their contact details. The address will automatically be populated for you.</P>
<P>If <STRONG>Other </STRONG>  is selected from the drop down list, the contact boxes below will be 
enabled, and you will need to input the details as required.</P>
<P>Click <STRONG>OK </STRONG>  when completed.</P>
